---
title: Beef Kofta Mezze Plate with Fattoush Salad & Lemon Pepper Fries
description: Turn a weeknight meal into a fun feast with this mixed platter of beef kofta, a fresh salad studded with pita crisps and creamy coriander yoghurt. Lemon pepper fries add the perfect finishing touch for a plate of tasty treats where every bite is different!
